 MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">a</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">*</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-stack" style="vertical-align: -0.157em;"><span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 70.7%; padding-bottom: 0.255em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mn"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">−</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">a</span></span> <span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">n</span></span></span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 。</p><p><br>牛顿法的每次迭代仅使用减法和乘法。使用牛顿法，每次正确数字的个数都是平方的。因此，我们有 (Ops inv) = (* 5 4) = 20。</p><h2> If 语句 Final、逻辑和因果关系计算</h2><p><br>所以，经过我们前面的分析，我们发现 (Ops div) = 21 和 (Ops step) = (+ 9 (Ops inv)) = 29。因此，我们有 (Ops if) = (+ (Ops step) 3) = 32。</p><p>现在我们可以使用“if”来生成逻辑连接词（ <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\neg"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">期望</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>与 1 运算的 neg 相同）。 </p><figure class="image"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/zkfmhWQXsZweijmzi/d3mkcfo1o2tfjbvm9khz" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/zkfmhWQXsZweijmzi/apot1utyqns92aokq6gq 120w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/zkfmhWQXsZweijmzi/b9isqt3vjrhiygbxxesg 240w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/zkfmhWQXsZweijmzi/tfzlc8rrqgm8ubbhhuqw 360w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/zkfmhWQXsZweijmzi/dewitj0g7ibf0quksvk2 480w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/zkfmhWQXsZweijmzi/dqza2jpxom8he89dolio 600w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/zkfmhWQXsZweijmzi/xxat8tok6p3amnhe3x0w 720w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/zkfmhWQXsZweijmzi/vhkbbnibezq666p8sapd 840w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/zkfmhWQXsZweijmzi/xfwdws86izqnrpaxzh0e 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/zkfmhWQXsZweijmzi/tlg4smh4pctmdeskcqnx 1080w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/zkfmhWQXsZweijmzi/htj8jjn7dba9swgdhvbz 1169w"></figure><h2>布尔值的因果关系计算</h2><p>TODO：然后对“或非或”、“如果-与”进行因果关系计算</p><h2>导数估计</h2><p><br>当我们能够访问导数时，将除法添加到我们的运算库中也为使用牛顿方法打开了大门，使我们能够找到可微函数（例如多项式）的零点。</p><p>此外，即使我们没有封闭形式，除法也使我们能够估计梯度。对于一些小的固定<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="h"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">h</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ，我们可以定义梯度估计 grad = <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\lambda"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">λ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> f x 。 (div(-(f(+xh))(fx))h)。此梯度估计的操作成本为 (Ops grad) = (Ops (list div - +)) = (+ 21 2 1) = 24。</p><p>有了这个梯度估计，我们就可以使用 Descend = <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\lambda"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">λ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> x <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\mu"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">μ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>来模拟梯度下降步骤。 (- x ( <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="*"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">*</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\mu"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">μ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> (grad fx)))<br>梯度下降步骤的操作成本为 (Ops Descend) = (Ops (list - * grad)) = (+ 2 1 24) = 27。考虑到这些操作的成本，决定使用 n 个步骤最小化某些函数(* 27 n) 次操作的下降取决于替代方案的成本。</p><p>回到因果关系的中心主题，在编程语言 lambda 演算 + {+, *, relu} 的背景下，我们最终可以声明 ( <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\lambda"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">λ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> x. x) 导致 ( <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\lambda"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">λ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> x. (* 2 x)) 大于( <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\lambda"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">λ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> x.(* 2 x)) 导致 ( <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\lambda"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">λ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> x.x)，因为 Ops ( <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\lambda"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">λ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> x.(* 2 x)) = 1 并且 Ops ( <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\lambda"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">λ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span> x.(div x 2)) = 21。</p><p>请注意，在确定<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="p_2"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">p</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>的复杂性时，我们没有明确使用<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="p_1"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">p</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>作为原语，因为 Ops <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="p_1"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">p</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> = Ops <span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="p_2"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">p</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> = 1。因此，将<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="p_1"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">p</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>作为成本 1 基本情况添加到 Ops 中是多余的。但希望算法是清楚的。</p><h1>通过近似得出因果关系</h1><h2><br>幂级数与分段线性以及递归的旁白</h2><p>也许此时您会认为许多函数的表示形式都很愚蠢：神经网络最终只会以分段线性方式拟合所有内容。我认为这可能是真的，特别是对于基本示例和小型网络。但我可以想象，更大的神经网络最终将学习用于常见操作的有效数据结构，也许我们可以根据数据结构的相对操作数量来预测何时会出现哪些数据结构。</p><p>让我们具体考虑一下<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="e^x"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">e</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sup" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: 0.513em; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mi" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">x</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 。</p><p>现在，我想讨论我们不考虑相等性，而是考虑<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="p_2"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-msubsup"><span class="mjx-base"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">p</span></span></span> <span class="mjx-sub" style="font-size: 70.7%; vertical-align: -0.212em; padding-right: 0.071em;"><span class="mjx-mn" style=""><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>近似值的保真度的情况。然后我们可以比较分段线性拟合的预期误差 (TODO)</p><p>考虑这个问题：我可以设想在神经网络内使用函数的几种不同表示。以<span><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="e^x"><span class="mjx-mrow